<title>zǒng shì duǎn zàn de xiāng jù 迦南391</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zǒng shì duǎn zàn de xiāng jù, zhǎng zhǎng de bié lí dàn wǒ bù huì wàng jì zài zhǔ lǐ zài zhǔ lǐ zhù fú nǐ
 xiān zǔ yǐ huí jiā wǒ men zhèng zài lǚ tú yǔ zhǔ tóng xíng zhōng xīn dào dǐ nǐ qiān wàn bié wàng jì
 jì yǒu fēn lí fēn lí jiù yòu xiāng jù xiāng jù xǔ nuò zài qián fāng de lù shàng yī dìng néng jiàn dào nǐ
 lù chéng bù yuǎn nǎ gāng qiáng cái hé shén xīn yì zhù nǐ píng ān zhù nǐ xìng wàng fán shì shùn lì.</lyrics>
</song>